aces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03009ac6e0a553d2a83ec81276968e41b3a4ca08","tid":1494573,"uid":276110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"不單止要見證支共倒台，重要見證支那瓦解，分裂成根據不同語言歷史風俗文化而建立嘅眾多小國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859003dc9029d19fb5f6ca5c315346bd75926c5c","tid":1494573,"uid":276110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"但願亞洲東面呢一大片土地上，<span style=\"color: red;\">永遠</span>唔再出現一個統一大國。咁嘅統一大國一定會行使法西斯主義，不斷吞噬週邊民族。"},{"pid":"d6ac113df67347c0fe034dec56735a86f1c55ace","tid":1494573,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3631249f24af96667ba56ebbd78a74067efb59","tid":1494573,"uid":305357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:07:00.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n<br />\n大部分蝗蟲支那狗真係唔死都冇用<br />\n邊到有蟲邊到就不得安寧，<br />\n周街屎尿屁，日日睇假新聞大聲夾惡<br />\n講唔掂就郁手，將本地人變到二等公民<br />\n<br />\n嚴重破壞地球生物既自然發展<br />\n一日有支那人，文明社會只會不斷倒退<br />\n<br />\n扔個炸彈落仆街中共到<br />\n所有共軍，黨員，藍絲，建制保皇一齊死<br />\n死剩返小部分中國人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如維權律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}